    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A beautiful, cloudless day on the ocean. The hustle and bustle of the crew's activities ring out in an endless drone. The salt spray on the sundried skin - invigorating. Wait, you're facing the wrong way. Turn around...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An intense storm cloud, almost black with menace, looms above the world. And we're heading straight for it...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We must prepare the ship and ourselves for whatever we find inside.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A 30-40 minute interactive, mystery-laden story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Explore a strange pirate ship to find and roll up all the flags and sails. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Interact with oddball denizens, and navigate underwater mazes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Intricately detailed artwork and animation, that will move you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A collection of weird and wonderful characters, some of which love eating things that aren't food. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Whoa! Some action. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Disturb a parrot, pet a cat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- An original soundtrack by magicdweedoo, that shifts the fibres of the soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BEST EXPERIENCED WITHOUT DISTRACTIONS, WITH NOISE-CANCELLING HEADPHONES.</p>",
